#   6. Amazon Bedrock removal (provider, auth, SigV4, catalog)
#   7. codex-feedback removal from core client
#   8. ~/.omnix home dir (with ~/.codex migration fallback)
#   9. Reasoning effort -> DeepSeek thinking mode mapping
